    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Looking for a reliable ride that still looks great on the road? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really nice shape, runs smoothly, and has been well-loved over the years. Whether you're commuting to work or heading out on a weekend road trip, this beauty is ready for its next adventure. Come by, take it for a spin, and see for yourself why I\u2019ve enjoyed it so much!",
