    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s build featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six mated to a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. The valvetrain is exceptionally quiet following a recent shim adjustment, and the VANOS system has been fully overhauled with upgraded seals and a cryo-treated hub. To ensure chassis integrity, the rear subframe mounting points have been reinforced\u2014a critical preventative measure for this platform. It retains its factory M-variable limited-slip differential and sits on refreshed bushings with Bilstein B6 dampers for precise turn-in and mid-corner stability. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the mechanical synchronization and throttle response are sharp, making this a quintessential driver-spec example.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Used vehicle in good condition. Engine runs well. Interior is clean. Minor cosmetic wear on exterior. Maintenance records available.",
